<h2>What is Chivy?</h2>
<p><em>Chivy</em> is a simple arcade game with logic elements. It requires of players high attention divisibility, skillful hands and quick thinking.</p>
<p><em>Chivy</em> can be played by many players on one computer (up to 4 players), through network or with computer opponents (6 difficulty levels). There are some maps included, but it is also possible to generate a random one.</p>
